Glad to join the conversation about ‘Shaping Today’s Generation For An Equal Tomorrow’ at the
#WeSeeEqual summit, organized by @proctergambleindia. 

The discussion brought to light the role of representation and imagery in conditioning us to have unconscious biases.

As a director, I believe on-screen representation plays a key role in how our society perceives gender. 

#UnlearnBiases #UnleashEquality

“Sit like a lady” “Behave lady like” all ways society wants to mould and present us into the perfect woman. 
@vivo_india has a new film that shows us how consistently we are asked to change our pose and then tells us the only pose women should strike is the Equal Pose! 
I ♥️ It. 

Watch the entire film on vivo India's YouTube and Social handles.
